en_211608_0	One more meditation programme, initiated by the Directorate of Psychological Operations got underway on Wednesday (8) at Kanduboda, Baunseth Mental Wellness Vipassana Meditation Centre.
en_211608_1	This meditation programme was conducted by Ven Diyasenpura Vimala Thera, as one more phase under the Lakmini Spiritual Advancement Programme.
en_211608_2	63 Army troops and 19 Naval troops including two Officers attended this programme, meant for spiritual advancement.
en_211608_3	Director Psychological Operations, Brigadier Athula Hannedige supervised this programme.
